154
00:12:48,040 --> 00:12:48,920
Talking-stage?

155
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,040
Yeah.

156
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:55,160
Once we get to know each other better,

157
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,240
