198
00:16:19,920 --> 00:16:21,120
Next,

199
00:16:22,280 --> 00:16:25,200
push it in like this,

200
00:16:25,200 --> 00:16:27,760
then pull it back out like this.

201
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:29,840
Then pull it out.

202
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:33,320
Oops.

203
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:36,520
Oh.

204
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:37,680
Hey.

205
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:39,320
Ah?

206
00:16:39,560 --> 00:16:40,720
Okay. Like this?

207
00:16:41,560 --> 00:16:43,520
