218
00:17:05,079 --> 00:17:07,079
Come on, show me a picture.

219
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:08,480
Please? Please?

220
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:09,480
Stop, stop, stop, stop.

221
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,079
Ahem.

222
00:17:10,079 --> 00:17:11,760
