274
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:53,080
Oh.

275
00:19:53,520 --> 00:19:55,080
I got pricked by a sewing needle.

276
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:57,280
Are you sure?

277
00:19:58,640 --> 00:19:59,440
What?

278
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:01,080
